data.description: OURAY, CO...Nicknamed "The Switzerland of America" and home to arguably most breathtaking mountain scenery, best hiking & restaurants in  Colorado.  This property though...the most charming home, tucked near the mountainous hillside on a corner lot RIGHT OFF OF THE RIVER. NEWLY REMODELED, this 2-bedroom, Den/Office & Gym boasts the most amazing features. The sellers added an amazing deck to decorate all seasons and enjoy your morning cup of coffee on. Upon entering the home, you will find a spacious great room covered in windows for ambient natural light and the most striking valley views. The newly remodeled kitchen has a "Mountain Modern" feel with newly re-faced cabinetry & a lay out that serves best for the space. The kitchen's vaulted ceilings carry into the dining and great room for the most amazing, spacious feel. The office/entertainment room serves many purposes and can easily be utilized as a retreat for guests. Down the hallway are the bedrooms including the guest bedroom & a cozy master suite. You’ll adore the large bathroom – double sinks and the gorgeous tiled walk-in steam shower. Also connected to the suite is a private room that the current owners use as a gym/workout area. The garage features an extra "workshop" in the back with plenty of storage. The owners have converted the outside space into a functional dream. Guests will love the front deck or side patio for relaxing and taking in the views along with the beautiful mountain landscaping. Have pets? There is a side/backyard that has a privacy fence and new turf for comfort and cleanliness. Need more room to store items outside? There is a covered carport area and storage shed. The property is perfectly located near the scenic Ouray North Corridor Trail and just minutes from town. Enjoy endless river walks as this properties location is next to none. This property is a  gem...do not miss out an opportunity to live in this gorgeous setting. Schedule your private showing today! *Please take a look at the Drone video under Non-Branded Virtual Tours to get a true feel for location and beauty of this home.
